shared_text:
Four Rivers Cultural Center and Museum
April 16 at 11:09 AM ¬∑

‚Äî LET‚ÄôS CREATE & CONNECT ‚Äî

Calling all lovers of art, in all its forms, The Four Rivers Cultural Center believes in the transforming power of art and its ability to celebrate and connect us to one another-- most especially in these times. We know most of you are now finding yourselves with extra time in your day, and we‚Äôd like to encourage you to use those minutes and hours to pull out all the stops and CREATE. Create the way you know how, share your amazing work with us, and in return, your work will be featured on our Facebook page. Plus, your name will get entered to win a $50 gift card. On May 8th, we‚Äôll draw names for 50 winners! Deadline to submit artwork is May 7th, but we‚Äôll be posting submitted artworks as we go. This is an all ages, all types of art submission. To submit or learn more about ART FOR ALL visit: https://bit.ly/frccart4all
